result.name: Mutational Spectrum of Some Cancer Related Genes in Leukemia Patients from Pakistan
result.description: This study is designed evaluate role of existing molecular markers and to identify new potential biomarkers for early detection and targeted therapy of leukemia.
result.center: Cancer Research Laboratory, Institute of Biochemistry, Biotechnology and BioInformatics, Faculty of Chemical and Biological Sciences, The Islamia University of Bahawalpur, Baghdad-ul-Jadeed Campus, Bahawalpur, Pakistan
